    Title Mplus Boostrapping

    MplusBootstrap.Rd

    Title Mplus Boostrapping

    MplusBootstrap(
  Model,
  type,
  first_path,
  second_path = NULL,
  multi_level,
  iv = NULL,
  m = NULL,
  w = NULL,
  xw = NULL,
  dv = NULL,
  first_stage_mod = NULL,
  level_one_mod = NULL,
  output = "Untitled",
  rep = 20000,
  conf = 95
)

    Arguments

    Model

    a list object containing the parameters of the model (from Mplus output file)

    type

    should choose from "med" "mod-med" or "med-mod"

    first_path

    the name of the first random path, left as 'fixed' when the path is not random (must be specified by the user)

    second_path

    the name of the second random path, left as 'fixed' when the path is not random (must be specified by the user)

    multi_level

    a binary variable indicating whether the specified is multi-level (must be specified by the user)

    iv

    the name of the independent variable

    m

    the name of the mediator

    w

    the name of the moderator

    xw

    the name of the interaction term

    dv

    the name of the dependent variable

    first_stage_mod

    a binary variable indicating whether the moderation effect is on the first path

    level_one_mod

    a binary variable indicating whether the moderation effect is on the first level

    output

    the name of the output image file (.png)

    rep

    the number of repetitions (default: 20000)

    conf

    the critical value used to generate confidence interval

    Value

    An image containing the distribution of the indirect effect and confidence interval
